lead_paragraph: Iowa coach Fran McCaffery walked off the court after the win and waved for his team to follow him to the locker room without shaking hands with North Dakota's players and coaches.

headline.print_headline: Iowa, McCaffery Walk Off Court Without Handshake for UND
